title: Counting Crows Studio Discography 1993-2012 [FLAC]
description:
Contains the albums:

August And Everything After (Deluxe Edition)
Hard Candy
Recovering The Satellites
Saturday Nights And Sunday Mornings
This Desert Life
Underwater Sunshine (Or What We Did On Summer Vacation)

*Please note Exact Audio Copy did not like track12 on August And Everything (Deluxe Ed.) disc1.  I encoded the track using Foobar.  I have cranked the track up on my pc with headphones and heard no hiccups.  All other tracks encoded normally.

Enjoy the music!
